    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014you won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent on it! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and it still has that fresh new-car smell. It drives like it just rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for absolute perfection, this is the one for you! Come take a look and fall in love!",
