    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a definitive example of the E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. This specimen features the S54B32 inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with high-tensile hardware, and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. The factory suspension remains taut, preserving the original kinematics and steering feedback. Presented in showroom condition with flawless paint depth and a pristine interior, this is a turn-key chassis for the uncompromising enthusiast.",
